xmlns:fr="http://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-005P.xml"><fr:frontmatter><fr:anchor>411</fr:anchor><fr:addr
type="user">sga1-i.4.5</fr:addr><fr:route>sga1-i.4.5.xml</fr:route><fr:taxon>Proposition</fr:taxon><fr:authors /><fr:number>I.4.5</fr:number><fr:parent>sga1-i.4</fr:parent></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>Let <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[f\colon  X\to  Y]]></fr:tex> be a morphism of finite type.
    Then the set of points where <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex> is étale is open.</fr:p>
  
    
    <fr:tree
toc="false"
numbered="false"
show-heading="true"
